10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:46,420
Wow... Buddy buddy Ride it out

11
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:48,420
大海一分為二也要 Ride it out

12
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:50,469
Buddy

13
